  "reference_number": "RUS1537",
  "remarks": "\nVitaly Pavlovich KHOTSENKO is a Russian official and politician appointed as Prime Minister of the so-called Donetsk People’s Republic in eastern Ukraine in June 2022. KHOTSENKO is an involved person under the Russia (Sanctions) (EU Exit) Regulations 2019 because he engages in and provides support for policies and actions which destabilise Ukraine and undermine or threaten the territorial integrity, sovereignty or independence of Ukraine.\n The trust services sanctions were imposed on 21/03/2023.",
